<Layout title="About - The High-Fidelity AI Collective">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="page-header text-center">
      <h1>About the Collective</h1>
    </header>
    
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>What is The High-Fidelity AI Collective?</h2>
      <p>
        We are a community of AI engineers, researchers, and MLOps specialists dedicated to solving the challenges of verifiable accuracy in high-stakes AI systems. Our focus is on mission-critical applications where reliability is not just a feature, but a requirement.
      </p>

      <h2>Who is this for?</h2>
      <p>
        This collective is for professionals working in fields where AI mistakes have serious consequences. This includes, but is not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>AI Engineers developing agentic systems for finance, healthcare, or aerospace.</li>
        <li>Researchers focused on formal verification and model provability.</li>
        <li>MLOps specialists building robust deployment and monitoring pipelines for critical infrastructure.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to Contribute</h2>
      <p>
        We welcome contributions from the community. For details on how to share your work, please see our <a href="/contributing">contributing guide</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
